Description:
	This program implements concept of message queue. The Server.c program create the shared memory and
	then listens for the changes made by client and displays on standard output.
	Note:- Please run Server program first in a terminal and then run Client program in different terminal. 	Write a character in Client terminal and receives the same in Server terminal.  


Steps to compile
[1] make
	compiles Server.c program first as this creates shared memory and then compiles Client.c
[2] make clean
	clean up 

Output

	Client Terminal 		
./Client 
s
a
g
a
r
b
o
r
s
e
q

	Server Terminal
./Server 
s 
a 
g 
a 
r 
b 
o 
r 
s 
e 
q
